e viklang assistance scheme of Haryana Labour Welfare fund, labour board provides Rs. 1.5 to 3 lakh on permanent disability of labourers at worksite. The eligibility criteria to avail Haryana Labour Disability Assistance Scheme are as follows:-Eligibility / \u092a\u093e\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0924\u093eMembership Years / \u0938\u0926\u0938\u094d\u092f\u0924\u093e \u0935\u0930\u094d\u09371Apply Frequency / \u0906\u0935\u0947\u0926\u0928 \u0915\u0940 \u0938\u0940\u092e\u093e1Scheme For / \u0907\u0938 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090fAllContinue After Death / \u092e\u0943\u0924\u094d\u092f\u0941 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0926 \u091c\u093e\u0930\u0940NoLabour Welfare Fund Haryana Disability Assistance Scheme 2019 is available for all registered workers of the Haryana state who suffers from permanent disability due to any accident at worksite.Haryana Labour Department Disability Assistance Scheme ConditionsPeople can follow the below mentioned conditions to avail financial aid under Labour Welfare Board Disabled Assistance Scheme in Haryana:-All the labourers must be registered and have permanent membership / subscription.In the identity certificate of the registered laborers, registration fees and updated subscription amount is to be mentioned.Candidates must submit the permanent Disability Certificate from the Health department of Haryana govt.All the disabled persons needs to apply online for Handicapped Assistance Scheme of Haryana Labour Department within 1 year of occurrence of disability. This assistance scheme for disabled persons has the main motto to create the best environment for the registered workers.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: hrylabour.gov.in  at  "}